<title>NEW ZEALAND: Hartley to replace Hancox as LWR chairman.</title>
<headline>Hartley to replace Hancox as LWR chairman.</headline>
<dateline>WELLINGTON 1997-07-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>LWR Industries Ltd said on Tuesday it had appointed Jon Hartley, New Zealand chief executive officer of Brierley Investments Ltd (BIL), as its chairman, replacing Bruce Hancox who is to step down from the chair due to personal commitments.</p>
<p>In a statement the company said Hartley would join the board and Hancox would remain on it, thus returning the total number on LWR's board to seven.</p>
<p>--Wellington newsroom +64 4 471 4273</p>
